ConditionType.description: Specifies the match criterion this condition defines - eg

IpPrefix.description: Used in conjunction with MaskLengthRange to specify the IP Prefix to match on when the ConditionType is MatchDstIpPrefix/MatchSrcIpPrefix.

MaskLengthRange.description: Used in conjuction with IpPrefix to specify specify the IP Prefix to match on when the ConditionType is MatchDstIpPrefix/MatchSrcIpPrefix.

MatchProtocol.description: Protocol to match on if the ConditionType is set to MatchProtocol
